If you are looking for a great Brunch, Yuca is the place. For $14.00 you can get a coffee, a drink and great food. They have wonderful selection of dishes to choose from (you have to try the Crab cake Benedict or the Arepa Benedict) . The brunch drinks are the best - big , strong and very tasty the only problem is that some times it is get very busy and Â you have to wait for a few minutes , BUT ...it's worth any second of your time .
